00:00:05,410 --> 00:00:06,730
买一
Numero uno.

2
00:00:18,290 --> 00:00:20,960
- 好了 - 让他2分钟后过来
- You're on. - Send him over to me in two minutes.

3
00:00:25,690 --> 00:00:29,080
常输的人也会有赢的时候
Although the joker could turn out to be the ace in the pack.

4
00:00:30,730 --> 00:00:32,840
赢了 厉害
Get in there,my son!

5
00:00:37,730 --> 00:00:39,370
不能把他们全赢光啊 Joe
Can't win them all,Joe.

6
00:00:42,770 --> 00:00:44,000
有问题?
Problem?

7
00:00:45,370 --> 00:00:47,040
那人是我丈夫
That's my husband.

8
00:00:49,810 --> 00:00:51,450
谢谢各位
Thank you,chaps.

