give it to him.

711
00:51:21,850 --> 00:51:23,810
真不敢相信你会这样做
I can't believe you're doing this.

712
00:51:23,890 --> 00:51:27,170
Stacie 无论他跟你说什么 别相信啊
Stacie,whatever he's promised you,don't fall for it.

713
00:51:33,330 --> 00:51:36,130
Stacie 我问你 我求你了
Stacie,I'm asking you,I am begging you...

714
00:51:36,490 --> 00:51:38,370
别这样做
please do not do this.

715
00:51:38,810 --> 00:51:41,370
我们没你了怎么办?
What the hell are we going to do without you?

716
00:51:42,770 --> 00:51:44,120
对不起
I'm sorry.

717
00:51:47,690 --> 00:51:50,250
我又赢你了吧?
Not the only thing I won off you again,is it?

718
00:52:03,770 --> 00:52:05,200
你赢我了?
You "won" me?

719
00:52:07,610 --> 00:52:10,520
好像我是个奖品似的
Makes it sound like I'm a prize in some raffle.

720
00:52:10,850 --> 00:52:12,970
对 可是你是最好的啊
Yeah,but you'd be the first prize.

721
00:52:15,290 --> 00:52:18,570
- 谢谢 - 只是开个玩笑 没关系吧?
- Thanks. - It's a joke.Does it matter?

722
00:52:19,970 --> 00:52:22,170
最重要的是我们又一起了
The main thing is that we're back together again.

723
00:52:22,250 --> 00:52:24,050
有关系
It matters to me.

724
00:52:24,650 --> 00:52:26,370
你是这样看我的啊 Jake?
Is that how you see me,Jake?

725
00:52:26,450 --> 00:52:29,650
就像个奖杯 好让你能在人家面前炫耀啊?
As a trophy you can show off to your friends when it suits you?

726
00:52:29,730 --> 00:52:30,720
不是,Stace
Come on,Stace.

727
00:52:30,810 --> 00:52:32,800
你一直都是那么想的 对吧?
That's what this has all been about,hasn't it?

728
00:52:32,890 --> 00:52:34,690
- 什么? - 你就知道钱 就知道赢
- What? - Money,winning...

729
00:52:34,770 --> 00:52:36,680
把我从Mickey手上抢过来
getting one over on Mickey.

730
00:52:36,770 --> 00:52:38,840
你们两一样差劲
You're both as bad as each other.

731
00:52:38,930 --> 00:52:41,890
你根本不想要我的 对不?
It wasn't about wanting me back at all,was it?

732
00:52:42,090 --> 00:52:43,490
我当然想
Of course it was.

733
00:52:43,610 --> 00:52:46,330
我是说 想要我
I mean,really wanting me.

734
00:52:47,690 --> 00:52:49,410
是真的
Of course it was.

735
00:52:53,650 --> 00:52:54,930
那证明吧
Prove it.

736
00:52:56,650 --> 00:52:59,400
- 怎样证明? - 我对你那么重要
- How? - lf I mean so much to you...

737
00:52:59,730 --> 00:53:01,560
那把钱扔了
get rid of the money.

738
00:53:02,090 --> 00:53:06,050
来 如果你爱我 把钱扔了
Go on.If you love me,throw it out into the river.

739
00:53:06,530 --> 00:53:07,730
什么?
What?

740
00:53:12,690 --> 00:53:14,680
我想你不会的
I didn't think you would.

741
00:53:21,850 --> 00:53:23,170
好的
All right.

742
00:54:08,170 --> 00:54:09,490
满意了吧?
Satisfied?

743
00:54:12,610 --> 00:54:14,680
我还以为
There was a moment there...

744
00:54:15,330 --> 00:54:18,210
还以为你对我是真心的
when I thought that you were genuine.

745
00:54:20,130 --> 00:54:21,960
如果你是真的
And if you had been...

746
00:54:23,330 --> 00:54:26,320
谁会知道我们之间会发生什么啊?
who knows what might have happened between us?

747
00:54:27,850 --> 00:54:30,650
我真够笨的
I was stupid enough to think that you'd changed...

748
00:54:30,730 --> 00:54:33,800
你从来就没变过
but you will never,ever change.

749
00:54:36,450 --> 00:54:40,570
那些全是假钞 对不对?
That was the case full of fake money,wasn't it?

750
00:54:48,050 --> 00:54:49,530
再见 Jake
Goodbye,Jake.

751
00:55:02,210 --> 00:55:06,050
- 至少让我补偿一下你 - 我一点都不想要钱
- At least let me give you what I owe you. - I don't give a damn about the money.

752
00:55:06,130 --> 00:55:07,690
我从来就没想过要
I never did.

753
00:55:08,890 --> 00:55:10,560
走吧
Just get out.

754
00:55:44,730 --> 00:55:46,370
我的外套 Eddie
My coat,please,Eddie.

755
00:56:03,810 --> 00:56:07,170
Danny 她干吗拿了一叠假钱?
Danny,does her taking one of these mean anything to you?

756
00:56:07,450 --> 00:56:08,930
等一下
Hang on a second.

757
00:56:11,490 --> 00:56:13,130
我知道她在干吗了
I know what she's doing.

758
00:56:18,770 --> 00:56:20,120
糟了 Jake!
No,Jake!

759
00:56:22,970 --> 00:56:26,440
我发誓我不知道 我不知道他们会这样做
I swear I didn't know.I didn't know they were going to do that.

760
00:56:27,650 --> 00:56:28,880
调头
Change of plan.

761
00:56:43,610 --> 00:56:46,000
你回来了 真好
Good to have you back,my dear.

762
00:56:48,490 --> 00:56:51,240
你就是能突发奇想
You always could think on your feet,Stace.

763
00:56:51,530 --> 00:56:53,600
Stacie就知道她要干什么的
Stacie knew what she was doing.

764
00:56:53,970 --> 00:56:56,690
- 我从未怀疑过她 - 很高兴听到这
- I never doubted her. - Glad to hear it.

765
00:56:57,810 --> 00:56:59,720
我们该等等Danny吗?
Shouldn't we wait for the kid?

766
00:57:00,050 --> 00:57:02,200
最好等一下 不然他会生气的
Yeah,better had.He'll only sulk.

767
00:57:04,370 --> 00:57:07,330
要等一下 他去拿钱了
Yeah,he might be a little while.He's gone fishing.

768
00:57:09,050 --> 00:57:12,600
- 正上来 - 好了
- On his way up. - Here we go.

769
00:57:13,770 --> 00:57:17,210
那么 你到底干了什么?
So,what exactly have you been up to?

770
00:57:17,290 --> 00:57:20,970
我只是以牙还牙吧了
Let's just say I've been dotting the "I's" and crossing the "T's," that's all.

771
00:57:21,050 --> 00:57:22,330
Ash?
Ash?

772
00:57:24,050 --> 00:57:26,330
我知道你也不想
I understand if you don't want to do this...

773
00:57:26,410 --> 00:57:28,530
但只有你跟他最熟悉了
but you know him better than anybody else.

774
00:57:28,610 --> 00:57:29,810
继续说
Go on.

775
00:57:30,090 --> 00:57:33,560
Jake给你留下了些什么让你感触的东西?
First,what were these thoughtful touches that Jake left you?

776
00:57:33,650 --> 00:57:36,250
房子卖了之后
Well,after selling the house...

777
00:57:36,730 --> 00:57:39,250
也把我银行帐户也清了
and cleaning out the bank account...

778
00:57:44,130 --> 00:57:46,250
就留给我一盘仙人掌
all he left me was a cactus...

779
00:57:47,810 --> 00:57:49,800
一张Phil Collins的CD...
a Phil Collins CD...

780
00:57:53,450 --> 00:57:56,050
和一份硬芝士
and a moldy piece of cheese.

781
00:58:00,850 --> 00:58:02,810
你都那样放了?
You did all that for me?

782
00:58:03,650 --> 00:58:06,610
对啊 他活该啊 不是吗?
Yeah,well,it's not like he didn't deserve it,is it?

783
00:58:07,530 --> 00:58:10,330
- 给没来的朋友? - 为什么不?
- To absent friends? - Why not?

784
00:58:10,850 --> 00:58:12,280
- 干杯 - 干杯
- Cheers. - Cheers.

785
00:58:20,450 --> 00:58:22,920
很好玩啊?谁把衣服带走了?
Very funny.Who nicked me clothes?

786
00:58:25,450 --> 00:58:27,330
可怜的Danny啊
Poor Danny!

787
00:58:28,450 --> 00:58:30,840
你就这样经过接待处啊?
Did you have to walk past the receptionist like that?

788
00:58:30,930 --> 00:58:32,280
是的 就这样
Yes,I did.

789
00:58:32,850 --> 00:58:34,920
但是我拿到她电话了喔
I did get her phone number,though.

790
00:58:36,290 --> 00:58:38,890
- 厉害 - 大家都做得好
- Well done,all. - Well done,boys.

791
00:58:44,170 --> 00:58:45,370
来
Open it up.

792
00:58:46,610 --> 00:58:48,040
Hello!
Hello!

